{"tid":1646334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅冠聰呢？2019年諾貝爾和平獎結果由阿比‧艾哈邁德奪得","createTime":"2019-10-11T09:12:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T10:43:48.000Z","uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac89c93eb1be1a28b53d9205e85b4641c198d083","tid":1646334,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:12:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20191011/1647310/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20191011%2F1647310%2F&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=ac07618e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20191011%2F1647310%2F&h=878092aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20191011/1647310/</a><br />\n<br />\n2019諾貝爾和平獎今天公布得主，由與厄利垂亞達成和平協議的衣索比亞總理阿邁德（Abiy Ahmed Ali）獲得殊榮。<br />\n今年諾貝爾已公布生醫獎、物理獎、化學獎，下周一將由經濟學獎壓軸公布。<br />\n獎項於每年12月10日（諾貝爾逝世紀念日）頒發。與其他在瑞典斯德哥爾摩頒發4個獎項不同，諾貝爾和平獎頒獎典禮是在挪威首都奧斯陸舉行，由挪威諾貝爾委員會主席頒獎，挪威國王監禮。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"961fa59809f0153b41aeac8bdfd2240eb293a726","tid":1646334,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c53e19e3e347305522fa693070ff564e7b04972","tid":1646334,"uid":135110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"5毛 遠阪凜#3020 手持至少6個連登帳號,請admin跟進<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1291657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1291657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2643febbae679214eed82de69b5c1a4e8a3d1a9f","tid":1646334,"uid":130563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T10:43:48.000Z","msg":"5毛 遠阪凜#3020 手持至少6個連登帳號,請admin跟進<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1291657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1291657</a><br />\n-